metadata.name: Two Halves
metadata.description:
Two Halves is an unpublished image, the first time shown here in Foundation. It represents humans' emotional and physical search to complete the second half, regardless of gender, identity, or background.
Humans, even as individuals already as a whole, call ourselves halves, and we permanently look for those genuine connections to feel complete as we are social and ready to mingle.

Image dimensions: 11771 x 11771 px
